      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the meatballs are browning, peel and finely dice<strong> </strong>your<strong> red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced onion</strong> and <strong>remaining grated garlic </strong>and cook for 6-7 min or until softened and slightly caramelised</p><p>Tip: Add an extra drizzle of oil if the pan's looking a little dry</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1656259930874-x200.jpg",
